{{Top|canon=Monofilament line}}
'''Monofilament cable''', also known as '''monofilament line''', was a liquid substance often ejected from [[Liquid-cable launcher/Legends|liquid-cable launchers]]. After launch and upon [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmospheric]] exposure, the monofilament solidified immediately into a tough yet lightweight and flexible cable. The tensile strength of a monofilament cable was generally strong enough to hold the weight of several [[Human/Legends|Humans]] and other beings.<ref name="Darth Maul: Shadow Hunter">''[[Darth Maul: Shadow Hunter]]''</ref>

